WHAT PROBLEM IT SOLVES
Replaces Fujifilm’s proprietary IDT with an open, verified mathematical
transform. Clarifies the distinction between F-Log and F-Log2, preventing
the use of incorrect inverse curves. Ensures that Fujifilm footage linearized
via GIOP matches the original scene light to within 10⁻⁶ relative error,
whether shot on a GFX100 II or an X-H2S.

